50|$|The theatre {{provides}} a 562-tiered-seat auditorium and balcony (400 <b>tiered</b> <b>seats</b> at ground-floor level; 138 tiered in the balcony; six private boxes each with four seats and a fridge), complimented by modern lighting and sound equipment. With a larger than normal designed stage, the theatre is {{designed as a}} flexible space for use either as a theatre or to accommodate conferences, presentations, award ceremonies and product launches.|$|R
